Type: Package
Package: doeR
Title: Generator and characterize designs of experiments in R (doeR)
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexandre", "Bohyn", , "alexandre.bohyn@kuleuven.be", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: Provides several functions to characterize regular designs in
    terms of aliasing and restrictions in the randomization (i.e.
    blocking, split-plotting, etc...). Also provides data sets containing
    designs coming from catalogs in the literature like Chen, Sun and Wu
    (1993) and Xu (2009).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ABohynDOE/doeR
BugReports: https://github.com/ABohynDOE/doeR/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Suggests: 
    covr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
